    "image": "products/25wc93148_2025.jpg",
    "short_description": "WARING commercial spice grinder for efficient spice processing. Heavy-duty construction, powerful motor for restaurants and food preparation facilities in Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>Professional Commercial Spice Grinder</h3><p>The WARING Commercial Spice Grinder is a powerful kitchen machine designed for efficient spice grinding in restaurants, hotels, and food preparation facilities throughout Kenya. This heavy-duty grinder processes whole spices into fine powders, ensuring fresh flavors and aromatic intensity for culinary applications. Built for demanding commercial environments, this grinder delivers reliable performance for high-volume spice processing.</p><h3>Key Features & Benefits:</h3><ul><li><strong>Powerful Motor:</strong> High-performance motor grinds spices efficiently</li><li><strong>Heavy-Duty Construction:</strong> Durable materials withstand commercial kitchen demands</li><li><strong>Consistent Results:</strong> Produces uniform grind texture for professional cooking</li><li><strong>Large Capacity:</strong> Processes substantial quantities for commercial needs</li><li><strong>Easy Operation:</strong> Simple controls allow efficient use by kitchen staff</li><li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Grinds various spices, herbs, and dried ingredients</li><li><strong>Safety Features:</strong> Protective mechanisms ensure safe operation</li><li><strong>Easy Cleaning:</strong> Removable components facilitate thorough cleaning</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>This spice grinder is essential equipment for restaurants, hotels, catering companies, and food preparation facilities in Kenya requiring fresh ground spices. Perfect for operations emphasizing authentic flavors, custom spice blends, and fresh ingredient preparation. Excellent for ethnic restaurants, specialty food operations, and culinary establishments.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
