    "short_description": "Electric sausage stuffer for commercial meat processing. Efficient equipment for butcheries and restaurants in Kenya.",
    "description": "<p>Electric Sausage Stuffer of 10L capacity with durable construction and a removable type canister ensures long-lasting durability as well as quick and simple cleaning. This sausage stuffer features large rubber feet and a heavy base to help prevent rocking during use. </p><p>Add this rugged, large-capacity sausage stuffer to your commercial kitchen or butcher shop to expand your sausage selection! This unit requires a 120V electrical connection for operation as an electric stuffer.</p><p>Has multiple tube attachments - included with this stuffer is a 1/2\", 3/4\", and 1\" stainless steel tubes, which allows you to easily adjust the desired size of your sausages. The tubes are simple to switch out, too, which increases the versatility in your operation.</p>",
    "technical_specification": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(81, 83, 101);\">Electric Sausage Stuffer of 10L capacity</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(81, 83, 101);\"><span class=\"ql-cursor\">﻿﻿</span>120V electrical connection</span></p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
  {
    "name": "TUMBLE MARINATOR",
    "sku": "IMG/HOT/00196",
    "brand": "ASTAR",
    "model_number": "BC-135L",
    "category": "Meat Processors",
    "price": 118962,
    "quantity": 2,
    "image": "products/1694467098__gallery_tumble-marinator.jpg",
    "short_description": "Commercial tumble marinator for rapid meat marinating. Time-saving equipment for restaurants and food service in Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>ASTAR BC-135L Tumble Marinator</h3><p>The ASTAR BC-135L Tumble Marinator is a commercial meat preparation machine designed for restaurants, hotels, and food service operations throughout Kenya. This innovative machine reduces marinating time from hours to minutes through a timed tumbling process. The flat edge of the barrel tenderizes the meat as it tumbles, accelerating the marinating process and allowing operators to serve freshly marinated product on demand.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Rapid Marinating:</strong> Reduces marinating time from hours to minutes</li><li><strong>Tenderizing Action:</strong> Flat edge of barrel tenderizes meat during tumbling</li><li><strong>On-Demand Service:</strong> Prepare freshly marinated product as needed</li><li><strong>Eliminates Waste:</strong> No need to over-prepare or worry about running out</li><li><strong>Stainless Steel:</strong> Durable, food-safe construction</li><li><strong>Timed Operation:</strong> Programmable tumbling cycles for consistency</li><li><strong>Large Capacity:</strong> Handles commercial volumes efficiently</li><li><strong>Easy Cleaning:</strong> Simple design facilitates sanitation</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Restaurants, hotels, catering operations, barbecue restaurants, and food service facilities in Kenya requiring rapid meat marinating capabilities. Ideal for operations serving grilled meats, marinated proteins, and specialty dishes requiring fresh, flavorful preparations.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
