    "description": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Experience the power of fresh, nutrient-rich juices with the CSE Centrifugal Juice Extractor. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">Designed to separate juice from pulp while squeezing, this stainless steel extractor makes it incredibly easy and quick to get natural, healthy juices from a wide variety of fruits and vegetables, including apples, carrots, beets, cucumbers, pineapples, oranges, kale, ginger, and many more.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">While the pure juice flows from one side of the equipment, the fruit waste, such as seeds and pulp, is efficiently expelled from the other side. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">This remaining pulp can even be creatively used in recipes for breads, jellies, cakes, and other delicious treats.</span></p><p><br></p>",
