    "description": "<p>The YC-53 is a stylish and compact under-counter wine cooler designed to keep your collection perfectly chilled. With a 53L capacity and room for up to 24 bottles, it’s ideal for both personal and professional use.</p><ul><li>Temperature Zone: Single, with adjustable settings from 5°C – 19°C</li><li>Cooling System: Reliable R600A compressor for efficient and eco-friendly performance</li><li>Shelving: 3 beech wood shelves that cradle bottles securely and enhance presentation</li><li>Door Design: Elegant full-glass door for a modern look and easy viewing</li><li>Rated Power: 75W, ensuring energy-efficient operation</li><li>Ambient Suitability: Works in environments from 10°C – 38°C</li><li>Weight: 28.5 kg, built sturdy yet compact for under-counter fitting</li></ul><p>Perfect for wine lovers, home bars, and restaurants, the YC-53 combines functionality, durability, and sleek design to preserve your wines at their best.</p>",
    "technical_specification": "<ul><li>60cm beverage refrigeration/cooler – temperature zone: single ,</li><li>Volume : 53L</li><li>Bottle capacity : 24 bottles</li><li>Compressor: R600A</li><li>Shelf: 3 beech wood shelves</li><li>Door: full glass</li><li>Rated power: 75w</li><li>Ambient temperature: 10 – 38 c</li><li>Temperature range: 5-19 c</li><li>Wight: 28.5 kg.</li><li>Dimensions: 590x560x450mm</li></ul><p><br></p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
