    "image": "products/1731573493__gallery_Capture.jpg",
    "short_description": "700mm countertop heated display by HDS. Compact professional food warmer for snacks and hot pastries in Kenyan food service operations.",
    "description": "<h3>HDS HDSHDN-26 Heated Display Counter Top - 700mm</h3><p>The HDS HDSHDN-26 is a compact 700mm countertop heated display unit built for food service operations in Kenya that need reliable hot food presentation in a space-saving format. This professional warmer is perfect for small cafes, kiosks, and delis where counter space is limited but a hot food display is essential for sales. The unit keeps a well-curated selection of savoury snacks, pastries, and hot foods at ideal serving temperature throughout the day, minimising waste and maximising customer satisfaction.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Compact 700mm Width:</strong> Space-saving size for tight counter areas</li><li><strong>Consistent Heating:</strong> Reliable temperature for safe hot food service</li><li><strong>Glass Display Panels:</strong> Product visibility drives customer purchases</li><li><strong>Countertop Format:</strong> Elevates food to eye level at point of sale</li><li><strong>Easy Staff Access:</strong> Quick restocking without disrupting service</li><li><strong>Energy Efficient:</strong> Economical heating for small-capacity unit</li><li><strong>Easy to Clean:</strong> Smooth surfaces simplify daily sanitation</li><li><strong>HDS Quality:</strong> Commercial-grade heating performance</li><li><strong>Professional Appearance:</strong> Neat presentation for retail environments</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Small cafes, food kiosks, bakeries, petrol station shops, school canteens, and compact delis in Kenya. Excellent for displaying and maintaining temperature of samosas, pies, sausage rolls, pastries, fried snacks, and other ready-to-eat hot foods in limited counter space.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
