    "image": "products/1731574429__gallery_images.jpeg",
    "short_description": "900mm countertop heated food display by HDS. Medium-capacity warm showcase for hot snacks and pastries in Kenyan cafes and delis.",
    "description": "<h3>HDS HDSHDN-36 Heated Display Counter Top - 900mm</h3><p>The HDS HDSHDN-36 is a medium-capacity 900mm countertop heated display offering more product space for Kenya's busier cafes, delis, and food service operations. This professional warmer strikes the perfect balance between display capacity and counter footprint, accommodating a wider variety of hot foods while remaining practical for most service counter configurations. Consistent heating throughout the unit ensures that every product presented remains at safe and appetising serving temperatures from opening until the last sale of the day.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Medium 900mm Width:</strong> Greater variety without excessive counter space</li><li><strong>Consistent Heat Distribution:</strong> Even temperature across all display levels</li><li><strong>Glass Display:</strong> Full product visibility to maximise impulse sales</li><li><strong>Countertop Placement:</strong> Hot food at eye level for maximum appeal</li><li><strong>Multiple Shelf Levels:</strong> Organise different food types by category</li><li><strong>Easy Restocking:</strong> Staff access for quick product rotation</li><li><strong>Energy Efficient:</strong> Optimised heating reduces operating costs</li><li><strong>Easy Cleaning:</strong> Smooth interior for quick daily sanitation</li><li><strong>HDS Reliability:</strong> Commercial-grade performance for daily service</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Medium-sized cafes, bakeries, supermarket delis, hotel breakfast stations, staff canteens, and food courts in Kenya. Ideal for displaying a varied selection of hot foods including pies, samosas, sausage rolls, mandazis, spring rolls, and savoury pastries throughout service hours.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
