    "short_description": "Ultra-capacity 250-litre spiral mixer by HK-Redline. Maximum 100kg dough output for the largest bakery operations in Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>HK-REDLINE BM-100 Spiral Mixer - 250 Litres / 100kg Dough Capacity</h3><p>The HK-REDLINE BM-100 is the most powerful mixer in the HK-Redline BM range, offering a 250-litre bowl and 100kg dough capacity for Kenya's largest industrial baking and food production operations. This machine represents the pinnacle of commercial dough mixing, built for facilities where dough production volume is measured in hundreds of kilograms per day. Every aspect of the BM-100's design is engineered for maximum output, reliability, and operator safety under continuous industrial operation.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>250-Litre Bowl / 100kg Dough:</strong> Pinnacle industrial mixing capacity</li><li><strong>Maximum-Power Motor:</strong> Sustains full-load operation continuously</li><li><strong>Heavy-Duty Spiral System:</strong> Industrial kneading at 100kg scale</li><li><strong>Massive Throughput:</strong> Minimum cycles for maximum dough output</li><li><strong>Industrial Steel Frame:</strong> Built for the most demanding environments</li><li><strong>Two-Speed Drive System:</strong> Controlled dough development stages</li><li><strong>Comprehensive Safety:</strong> Full guard systems for operator protection</li><li><strong>Engineered for Longevity:</strong> Components selected for continuous heavy use</li><li><strong>HK-Redline Excellence:</strong> The most capable mixer in the range</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Industrial baking facilities, large-scale food manufacturers, wholesale bread factories, and major institutional food production in Kenya. The ultimate mixer for operations supplying bread, rolls, and pastry products at the highest commercial volumes to supermarket chains, hotel groups, and large-scale food distribution networks.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
  {
    "name": "CAKE MIXER PLANETARY 7 LITRES H-KITCHEN",
