    "short_description": "Compact 7-litre planetary cake mixer by HK-Redline. Versatile commercial mixer for cakes, creams, and pastries in Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>HK-REDLINE HK-B7 Planetary Mixer - 7 Litres</h3><p>The HK-REDLINE HK-B7 is a compact 7-litre planetary mixer ideal for small bakeries, cafes, and pastry operations across Kenya. Unlike spiral mixers designed for dough, planetary mixers use a planet-orbit motion where the attachment rotates on its own axis while simultaneously orbiting the bowl — making them exceptionally versatile for a wide range of baking tasks. From whipping cream and beating eggs to mixing cake batter and light pastry, this compact unit handles it all with ease.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>7-Litre Bowl:</strong> Compact yet capable for small-batch work</li><li><strong>Planetary Action:</strong> Versatile mixing for cakes, creams, and batters</li><li><strong>Multiple Attachments:</strong> Flat beater, dough hook, and wire whisk</li><li><strong>Variable Speed:</strong> Multiple speeds for different mixing tasks</li><li><strong>Compact Design:</strong> Space-efficient for smaller kitchens</li><li><strong>HK-Redline Reliability:</strong> Commercial-grade motor for daily use</li><li><strong>Easy Bowl Removal:</strong> Quick changeover between tasks</li><li><strong>Versatile Application:</strong> Cakes, creams, icings, pastry, and light doughs</li><li><strong>Accessible Price:</strong> Professional quality at competitive cost</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Small bakeries, pastry kitchens, cafes, hotel restaurants, and catering operations in Kenya. Excellent as a dedicated mixing station for cake batters, buttercreams, mousses, meringues, and light pastry doughs alongside spiral mixers used for bread production.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
