    "short_description": "Roller Grill RFG 12 commercial electric fryer delivering professional high-volume frying performance for fast food restaurants and catering kitchens in Kenya.",
    "description": "<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The professional gas fryer RFG 12 is particularly suitable for&nbsp;the cooking of fresh and frozen food for take-away.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The&nbsp;filtering basket-holder&nbsp;placed at the bottom of the stainless steel tank has a&nbsp;dual function:</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">-&nbsp;This filter&nbsp;recovers important&nbsp;residues of frying</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">-&nbsp;This grid&nbsp;allows&nbsp;to fry without basket&nbsp;large pieces such&nbsp;as donuts or whole fish for \"fish and chips\" menus</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">This&nbsp;gas deep fat fryer&nbsp;is equipped with a double ramp of&nbsp;very powerful radiants&nbsp;placed under the&nbsp;stainless steel tank.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The&nbsp;Piezo ignition&nbsp;is made by simply pressing both ignition and adjustment buttons. The pilot light makes it possible&nbsp;to control the arrival of the gas&nbsp;and the good lighting of the fryer. The gas is evacuated by the&nbsp;back pipe.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Maintenance&nbsp;is carried out&nbsp;safely&nbsp;thanks to a&nbsp;stainless steel drain tap.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">This&nbsp;modular fryer&nbsp;can be installed on a work surface or mounted on the&nbsp;stainless steel cabinet&nbsp;MS-RFG 12.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Features: Piezo ignition button, thermocouple and pilot light, 2 very powerful burners, draining device, basket, adjustable feet. Stainless steel lid.</p><p><br></p>",
