    "description": "<h3>Crem Coffee Brewer with 2 Decanters – CQM2</h3><p>The Crem CQM2 is a dual-decanter professional coffee brewer that delivers twice the serving capacity of a single-decanter unit — ensuring a continuous supply of fresh-brewed coffee at hotel breakfast buffets, large restaurants, and high-volume beverage service operations across Kenya. With two decanters always available, service staff can replenish one while the other is in active service, eliminating coffee service gaps during busy periods.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Dual Decanter System:</strong> Two glass decanters provide double capacity and continuous service availability</li><li><strong>Simultaneous or Sequential Brewing:</strong> Brews into one decanter while the other is in service</li><li><strong>Dual Warming Plates:</strong> Keeps both decanters of coffee at optimal serving temperature</li><li><strong>Precise Brewing Temperature:</strong> Consistent extraction for excellent coffee quality in every batch</li><li><strong>Stainless Steel Professional Body:</strong> Durable, hygienic, and presentable for front-of-house service</li><li><strong>High-Capacity Water System:</strong> Handles the water volume needed for continuous dual-decanter brewing</li><li><strong>Easy-to-Use Controls:</strong> Simple operation for consistent results from any catering staff</li><li><strong>Crem Commercial Reliability:</strong> Trusted professional brand for demanding hospitality environments</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Hotels, large restaurants, conference facilities, and high-volume commercial catering operations in Kenya that need continuous, uninterrupted fresh-brewed coffee service during breakfast, events, and throughout busy daily service periods.</p>",
    "status": "draft"
  },
