  {
    "name": "THERMO BOX 6 GN HEATED",
    "sku": "IMG/BUF/00186",
    "brand": "HK-REDLINE",
    "model_number": "CPWK090-31",
    "category": "Food Transport",
    "price": 181750,
    "quantity": 4,
    "image": "products/1729260249__gallery_Mt.jpg",
    "short_description": "HK-Redline CPWK090-31 heated thermo box for 6 GN containers, combining active heating with insulated transport for hot food delivery at large catering events across Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>HK-Redline Heated Thermo Box 6 GN – CPWK090-31</h3><p>The HK-Redline CPWK090-31 Heated Thermo Box is a large-capacity, actively heated insulated food transport unit accommodating up to 6 standard GN containers. Unlike passive thermo boxes that rely solely on insulation, this model incorporates an active electric heating system that continuously maintains food at correct hot serving temperatures during transport and holding — making it ideal for large off-site catering operations, outdoor events, and banquet service across Kenya where food must arrive genuinely hot.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>6 GN Container Capacity:</strong> Large volume for transporting a complete hot meal range in a single unit</li><li><strong>Active Electric Heating:</strong> Built-in heating element actively maintains food at hot serving temperature during transport</li><li><strong>High-Density Insulated Shell:</strong> Combined active heating and insulation for superior temperature retention</li><li><strong>GN Standard Compatible Rails:</strong> Internal GN rails securely hold standard GN food pans during transport</li><li><strong>Temperature Control:</strong> Adjustable heating settings for different food holding temperature requirements</li><li><strong>Secure Locking Lid:</strong> Heavy-duty latch prevents lid opening and heat loss during transit</li><li><strong>Heavy-Duty Outer Casing:</strong> Impact-resistant body protects contents during outdoor and vehicle transport</li><li><strong>Carry Handles and Castors:</strong> Multiple carrying options for flexible maneuvering at event venues</li><li><strong>Food-Safe Hygienic Interior:</strong> Easy-to-clean surfaces maintain food safety standards post-service</li><li><strong>HACCP Compatible:</strong> Active heating supports compliance with hot food holding temperature requirements</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Large-scale catering companies, hotel outdoor event operations, school feeding programs, corporate event caterers, and commercial food service businesses in Kenya requiring a high-capacity actively heated thermo box for compliant, large-volume hot food transport and holding at off-site venues, outdoor events, and remote catering assignments.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
