    "short_description": "Sunnylux ED1100 food waste shredder disposer for hygienic, efficient disposal of food waste directly through the sink drain in commercial kitchens across Kenya.",
    "description": "<p>The ED1100 Food Sink Shredder Disposer is a powerful and reliable solution for managing kitchen waste with ease. Built with a <strong>1.5HP (1100W) permanent magnet DC motor</strong>, it delivers a high-speed performance of <strong>3200r/min</strong>, ensuring efficient and ultra-fine grinding of food scraps.</p><p><br></p><p>Featuring the advanced <strong>Cyclone™ Ultrafine Grinding System</strong>, this disposer breaks down waste quickly while reducing the risk of clogs. Its <strong>stainless steel grinding components</strong> guarantee durability and long-lasting performance, while the <strong>permanent antibacterial protection</strong> helps maintain hygiene in your kitchen.</p><p><br></p><p>For added safety, the ED1100 is equipped with a <strong>manual reset protector</strong> to guard against overloads and temperature spikes, providing peace of mind during heavy use.</p>",
    "technical_specification": "<ul><li>Voltage: AC220–240V, 50/60Hz</li><li>Motor Power: 1.5HP / 1100W permanent magnet DC motor</li><li>Motor Speed: 3200r/min</li><li>Grinding System: Cyclone™ Ultrafine for superior grinding performance</li><li>Grinding Components: High-quality stainless steel</li><li>Antimicrobial Protection: Permanent antibacterial technology</li><li>Safety: Manual reset protector for overload and temperature protection</li><li>Durable, hygienic, and designed for high-performance waste disposal</li></ul>",
    "status": "published"
  },
