    "description": "<ul><li>Rational Active Green Tabs (Green) for iCombi Pro &amp; iCombi Classic - 120/Case with special airfreight packing; </li><li>Thanks to the new formula the number of cleaner tabs can be reduced by up to 50 % depending on the cleaning operation. </li><li>Keeps both the cooking system and the environment clean: </li><li>The cleaner tab with its new formula is phosphate and phosphorous-free and reduces the quantity of cleaner by up to 50 %*. </li><li>Without compromising on cleaning power and hygiene. </li><li>Can perform an ultra-fast interim clean of the iCombi Pro in approx. 12 minutes</li></ul>",
    "technical_specification": "<ul><li>SODIUM CARBONATE\t20 - 50 %</li><li>SILICIC ACID, SODIUM SALT\t20 - 30 %</li><li>ALCOHOLS C 16 - 18, ETHOXYLATED\t1 - 5 %</li><li>DISODIUM METASILICATE\t1 - &lt;3 %</li></ul>",
    "status": "published"
  },
