    "image": "products/1693396613__gallery_7524187.jpg",
    "short_description": "TASKI Go UK vacuum cleaner — ultra-compact, lightweight professional vacuum for quick, agile everyday cleaning in hotels, offices, and commercial spaces across Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>TASKI Go UK</h3><p>The TASKI Go is the ultra-compact, portable professional vacuum cleaner from TASKI's trusted commercial cleaning range. Designed for speed and agility in everyday cleaning operations, the TASKI Go is ideal for quick vacuum tasks in hotel rooms, corridors, offices, and smaller spaces where a larger machine would be unnecessarily cumbersome. Lightweight and easy to carry, it empowers housekeeping staff to clean faster and more efficiently.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Ultra-Compact Design:</strong> Small, lightweight body for maximum agility in rooms, corridors, and tight spaces</li><li><strong>Portability:</strong> Easy to carry between rooms for fast-paced housekeeping operations</li><li><strong>Reliable Suction:</strong> Effective vacuuming performance on carpets and hard floors</li><li><strong>UK Configuration:</strong> UK plug and specification for immediate use</li><li><strong>TASKI Quality:</strong> Professional-grade durability and reliability built into a compact form factor</li><li><strong>Accessory Compatible:</strong> Works with TASKI Go accessory range for versatile cleaning applications</li><li><strong>Easy Maintenance:</strong> Simple bag and filter access for quick servicing between shifts</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Hotel housekeeping departments, boutique hotels, serviced apartments, guesthouses, and office cleaning teams across Kenya that need a fast, agile, portable vacuum cleaner for quick and efficient daily room cleaning and corridor maintenance.</p>",
    "status": "draft"
  },
