    "short_description": "TASKI Aero BP B Li-Ion cordless backpack vacuum — battery-powered professional backpack vacuum for cable-free, agile cleaning in large commercial environments across Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>TASKI Aero BP B Li-Ion – Cordless Backpack Vacuum</h3><p>The TASKI Aero BP B Li-Ion is the battery-powered evolution of TASKI's acclaimed backpack vacuum cleaner. Combining the unmatched agility of a backpack design with the freedom of cordless Li-Ion operation, this professional vacuum cleaner eliminates cable management entirely — allowing cleaning teams to move seamlessly through large, complex spaces without the restriction or hazard of power cables.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Li-Ion Battery Power:</strong> Cordless operation for complete freedom of movement in any space</li><li><strong>Backpack Design:</strong> Worn on the back for maximum mobility and hands-free cleaning productivity</li><li><strong>Extended Run Time:</strong> Li-Ion battery technology provides sustained runtime for extended cleaning shifts</li><li><strong>No Cable Hazards:</strong> Fully cordless eliminates trailing cable trip hazards in public spaces</li><li><strong>Powerful Suction:</strong> Battery-powered motor delivers consistent professional-grade suction performance</li><li><strong>Rapid Recharge:</strong> Li-Ion technology enables fast battery recharging for minimal downtime</li><li><strong>Ergonomic Harness:</strong> Comfortable, adjustable body harness for extended shift wear</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Airports, shopping centres, large hotels, hospitals, event venues, and professional cleaning companies across Kenya where cord-free operation is essential for safety, efficiency, and seamless movement through large or complex floor spaces.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
