    "description": "<h3>TASKI Vacumat 22 UK</h3><p>The TASKI Vacumat 22 is a professional wet and dry vacuum cleaner built for the demanding dual requirements of commercial liquid recovery and dry debris collection. Equally at home recovering spilled liquids from floors or vacuuming dry dust and debris, the Vacumat 22 is an essential multi-function cleaning tool for facilities management teams, hotel housekeeping, and commercial cleaning operations that encounter a wide variety of cleaning challenges daily.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Wet and Dry Capability:</strong> Recovers liquids and vacuums dry debris in a single, versatile machine</li><li><strong>22-Litre Capacity:</strong> Large tank for extended wet recovery or dry vacuuming without frequent emptying</li><li><strong>Powerful Motor:</strong> Strong suction performance for both wet liquid recovery and dry vacuuming</li><li><strong>UK Configuration:</strong> UK plug and specification for immediate commercial deployment</li><li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> TASKI build quality designed for daily professional cleaning use</li><li><strong>Easy Tank Emptying:</strong> Practical tank design for hygienic liquid disposal</li><li><strong>Accessory Compatible:</strong> Works with TASKI wet and dry vacuum accessory range</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Hotels, hospitals, restaurants, shopping centres, commercial kitchens, and facilities management companies across Kenya that need a reliable, high-capacity wet and dry vacuum cleaner for spill recovery, liquid collection, and dry debris vacuuming in demanding environments.</p>",
