    "short_description": "OEM Sheffield Chrome Wire Shelving 1220mm — heavy-duty chrome-plated wire shelving unit for versatile, well-ventilated storage in commercial kitchens and storerooms across Kenya.",
    "description": "<h3>OEM Sheffield Chrome Wire Shelving – 1220mm</h3><p>The OEM Sheffield Chrome Wire Shelving at 1220mm is a professional-grade heavy-duty wire shelving unit that combines strength, ventilation, and versatility for commercial storage environments. The chrome-plated wire construction promotes excellent airflow around stored goods — reducing moisture build-up, inhibiting mould, and keeping stored items fresher for longer. At 1220mm wide, this unit offers maximum storage capacity for busy commercial kitchens, storerooms, and food preparation areas.</p><h3>Key Features:</h3><ul><li><strong>Chrome-Plated Wire Construction:</strong> Durable chrome finish provides corrosion resistance and a clean, professional appearance</li><li><strong>1220mm Width:</strong> Full-width shelving for maximum commercial storage capacity</li><li><strong>Open Wire Design:</strong> Promotes excellent air circulation around stored goods for freshness and hygiene</li><li><strong>Heavy-Duty Load Capacity:</strong> Robust wire gauge and frame construction for heavy commercial storage loads</li><li><strong>Adjustable Shelf Positions:</strong> Flexible height configuration to suit different product storage requirements</li><li><strong>Easy to Clean:</strong> Open wire design allows easy cleaning and inspection of shelves</li><li><strong>Versatile Application:</strong> Suitable for dry storage, general storerooms, kitchen preparation areas, and back-of-house storage</li><li><strong>Modular Design:</strong> Can be combined with additional units for larger storage configurations</li></ul><h3>Perfect For:</h3><p>Commercial kitchens, hotel storerooms, restaurants, catering companies, supermarket back-of-house areas, and food service operations across Kenya that need high-capacity, well-ventilated, heavy-duty wire shelving for organized and hygienic storage.</p>",
    "status": "published"
  },
