    "short_description": "Antunes AQ-RO-600 reverse osmosis system — reliable water purification for professional coffee and beverage equipment in commercial kitchens across East Africa.",
    "description": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(35, 31, 32);\">Whether you need clean water to effectively operate your water-reliant kitchen equipment, or as a vital ingredient in your food and beverage production, the quality of the water coming out of your tap dramatically impacts your efficiency and final product. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(35, 31, 32);\">Rather than working around poor water quality, take control of your water by installing a commercial reverse osmosis system in your food service operation. </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(35, 31, 32);\">When you get this system installed, you will have high-quality water all year long for your patrons.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(35, 31, 32);\">You and your guest will appreciate the high water quality that you offer because everything will taste more delicious than it did before.</span></p>",
