    "image": "products/1741687230__gallery_5.png",
    "short_description": "",
    "description": "<h3><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">The HATTON HT-T2 under-counter dishwasher combines powerful cleaning capabilities with space-saving design for commercial kitchens where floor space is at a premium. This versatile unit features three programmable wash cycles (60/90/120 seconds) to accommodate various cleaning needs, from lightly soiled glassware to heavily soiled cookware.</span></h3><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">This professional dishwasher is designed to deliver consistent cleaning results while maximizing kitchen efficiency. Its robust construction and reliable performance make it an excellent choice for cafes, small restaurants, bars, and other food service operations seeking quality dishwashing capabilities in a space-efficient format.</span></h3><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Key Features:</strong></h3><ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Single door, front-opening design for easy access and loading</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Multi-function jet-style cleaning system for thorough washing</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Compact dimensions (600×600×800mm) ideal for installation under counters</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Flexible wash cycle options (60/90/120 seconds) for different soiling levels</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">30L capacity with 8L booster for efficient operation</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">ISO9001 certified for quality assurance</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Lightweight design at only 80kg net weight</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Water supply pressure range of 0.25-0.5MPa for optimal performance</span></li></ul><h3><br></h3>",
    "length": 600,
    "width": 600,
    "height": 800,
    "technical_specification": "<ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Model: HT-T2</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Capacity: 30L</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Type: Single Door Disinfection Cabinet</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Cabinet Door Style: Front-open</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Function: Multi-function</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Style: Jet</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Wash Cycle Options: 60/90/120 Second</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Water Supply Pressure: 0.25-0.5MPa</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Booster Capacity: 8L</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Dimensions: 600mm × 600mm × 800mm</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Max Washing Height: 320mm</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Net Weight: 80kg</span></li></ul>",
