    "short_description": "",
    "description": "<h3><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">The HATTON HT-Z1 is a high-performance restaurant hood type dishwasher engineered for commercial kitchens that require fast, efficient cleaning solutions. This professional-grade unit combines powerful washing capabilities with water efficiency to meet the demands of busy food service operations.</span></h3><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">﻿This commercial dishwasher provides exceptional cleaning performance while maintaining compact dimensions of 690mm × 780mm × 1475mm. With its 505mm entrance width and 420mm maximum washing height, the HT-Z1 accommodates a wide variety of dishware and kitchen utensils. This durable and reliable dishwasher is the perfect solution for restaurants, hotels, and catering services seeking to enhance their kitchen efficiency.</span></h3><h3><strong style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Key Features:</strong></h3><ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Single door disinfection cabinet with convenient front-open access</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Multi-function jet-style cleaning system for superior results</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Impressive 60 rack/hour washing capacity</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Water-efficient design using only 3 liters per rack</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Generous 21.5L water tank capacity</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">CE and ISO9001 certified for quality assurance</span></li></ul><h3><br></h3><h3><br></h3>",
